how brutal it is for you guys.

09:52.996 --> 09:54.970
People make fun of my haircut.

09:55.024 --> 09:57.796
Oh, if that's the worst
thing that's happened to you,

09:57.798 --> 09:59.852
you're dead when you
get into the real world.

09:59.877 --> 10:01.540
It's not that bad here at Fillmore.

10:01.565 --> 10:05.350
Ugh. You guys, you're giving
me nothing to work with.

10:05.875 --> 10:07.625
It's gonna get bad.

10:07.650 --> 10:11.046
When you get to sixth
grade, get boobs, cramps,

10:11.048 --> 10:13.582
whatever it is guys get,

10:13.584 --> 10:14.918
everything's gonna change.

10:14.920 --> 10:18.019
When that happens, remember
that you have a voice.

10:18.021 --> 10:20.055
And think of our group's name:

10:20.057 --> 10:23.443
Stop Teasing And Bullying. STAB.

10:23.445 --> 10:29.998
All: STAB! STAB! STAB! STAB! STAB! STAB!

10:30.000 --> 10:33.001
STAB! STAB! STAB! STAB! STAB!

10:33.655 --> 10:35.874
Ms. Snap, I drew you another picture.

10:37.007 --> 10:38.840
Why do you insist on making me ugly?

10:38.842 --> 10:41.002
What?
- I didn't pay $60 a week

10:41.004 --> 10:43.275
for a juice cleanse to have
my thigh gap go unnoticed.

10:43.855 --> 10:44.855
I'm on to you.

10:45.418 --> 10:47.355
I'm not gonna let you
bring me down, Debbie.

10:55.113 --> 10:58.523
This is a prime example
of institutional bullying.

10:58.525 --> 11:00.580
Gender specific bathrooms force students

11:00.582 --> 11:02.353
to prematurely classify themselves,

11:02.355 --> 11:04.020
when really gender's on a spectrum.

11:04.022 --> 11:07.123
I can relate. One time
I dreamt I had a dick.

11:07.125 --> 11:08.257
I do have one question though.

11:08.259 --> 11:10.242
How are they gonna know
which bathroom to use?

11:12.337 --> 11:13.648
Now they can use either.

11:14.203 --> 11:15.474
Don't you have a class right now?

11:15.476 --> 11:16.656
They're in silent free time.

11:16.658 --> 11:19.013
[all screaming]

11:19.015 --> 11:20.820
Come on. We've got five
more bathrooms to hit.

11:23.074 --> 11:25.926
Did you know you can
get HPV from fingers?

11:25.951 --> 11:28.077
