11:30.701 --> 11:32.683
Oh, nice. What was it for?

11:32.685 --> 11:34.545
Anal bleaching.

11:37.121 --> 11:38.896
Do you really think that you need that?

11:39.724 --> 11:40.715
Probably.

11:40.717 --> 11:42.058
Both: STAB! STAB! STAB!

11:42.060 --> 11:44.026
STAB! STAB! STAB! STAB! STAB! STAB!

11:44.028 --> 11:45.795
Oh, don't worry. That's, uh,

11:45.797 --> 11:47.163
that's our new anti-bullying club.

11:47.165 --> 11:49.165
Aren't they being a little aggressive?

11:49.167 --> 11:52.068
No. They're just standing
up for themselves.

11:52.070 --> 11:53.069
My mom says I can be President.

11:53.071 --> 11:55.250
You're too stupid to be the President.

11:55.252 --> 11:57.430
Oh, isn't that kid in your class?

11:57.432 --> 11:59.315
Yeah. That's Blake.

11:59.317 --> 12:00.500
Well, he's a bully.

12:00.525 --> 12:02.309
You need to call a
conference with his parents.

12:02.334 --> 12:03.342
Dumb bitch.

12:04.818 --> 12:06.021
Today.

12:06.865 --> 12:08.433
Because the bottom line is

12:08.435 --> 12:10.186
you can't break up with someone

12:10.188 --> 12:12.021
and still like all
their posts on Facebook.

12:12.497 --> 12:13.982
You need to give them closure.

12:14.521 --> 12:16.675
Just because one person's okay

12:16.677 --> 12:18.029
doesn't mean the other person is.

12:18.429 --> 12:19.921
For all you know, that other person

12:19.923 --> 12:21.585
could have been asked to
leave their pottery class

12:21.587 --> 12:23.833
at the learning annex
due to excessive crying

12:23.835 --> 12:26.829
<i>because the class kept reminding
them of the movie Ghost.</i>

12:27.906 --> 12:30.491
So what's the answer?

12:30.493 --> 12:32.868
Sorry. I got a little sidetracked.

12:36.782 --> 12:41.597
It's one.

12:41.599 --> 12:42.667
[knocking]

12:42.669 --> 12:44.238
Ms. Bennigan?
- Oh, Hot Dad.

12:44.263 --> 12:45.263
What?

12:46.685 --> 12:48.813
Yes? Hi. Hello.

12:48.815 --> 12:50.320
Are you Blake's dad?

12:50.322 --> 12:53.506
Yeah. You wanted to meet with me?

12:53.531 --> 12:56.766
Yes, thank you for coming in.

12:56.768 --> 13:00.525
Um, I wanted to talk
with you about some issues

13:00.527 --> 13:02.105
concerning Blake's behavior.

13:02.183 --> 13:03.316
Yeah.

13:03.998 --> 13:05.497
I was afraid of that ever since

13:05.530 --> 13:09.032
the, uh, change in our family situation.

13:09.347 --> 13:10.447
Oh.

13:10.449 --> 13:12.285
