13:12.830 --> 13:14.029
Uh...

13:15.219 --> 13:16.379
His mom left us.

13:16.404 --> 13:18.313
Oh.

13:19.226 --> 13:20.458
I'm so sorry.

13:20.483 --> 13:22.550
Oh, no. It's... it's fine.

13:22.575 --> 13:23.813
No, we'll be strong.

